transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you so much for calling Viagra at Score Blue.

Speaker 2: How can I help you today?

Speaker 1: Yes, I was calling to cancel my prescription.

Speaker 2: OK, sir, I can help you with this.

Speaker 1: Could you just provide me your full name and date of birth, please?

Speaker 2: Donnell Henderson, D-A-R-N-E-L-L, Henderson.

Speaker 1: Date of birth, June 7, 1965.

Speaker 2: Thank you so much.

Speaker 1: Bear with me while I pull up your account, all right?

Speaker 2: OK, sir, so I see here this prescription was for the 100 milligram Sildenafil, quantity of 10 each fulfillment.

Speaker 1: Does that sound accurate?

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: OK.

Speaker 2: So it looks here, were you having issues with the medication?

Speaker 1: Is it an auto-ship issue?

Speaker 2: How can I help you today?

Speaker 1: Well, really, I mean, I didn't know I was going to keep doing it.

Speaker 2: I thought I was going to just try it once.

Speaker 1: But then I looked on the phone where it is, did another prescription.

Speaker 2: I just wanted to try it.

Speaker 1: Oh, understood.

Speaker 2: Well, your refill here, Darnell, your refill here has not been assigned a tracking number.

Speaker 1: So I can put a cancel request in that for you.

Speaker 2: Because this is not a subscription.

Speaker 1: It just looks like that's how the doctor wrote it initially.

Speaker 2: So this one that was placed on the 24th, I can put a cancel request in and get you that refund once it's confirmed.

Speaker 1: Yes.

Speaker 2: OK.

Speaker 1: So let me go ahead and do that for you.

Speaker 2: Let me reach out to the pharmacy real quick.

Speaker 1: Give me one moment.

Speaker 2: OK.

Speaker 1: OK.

Speaker 2: So I went ahead and put a cancellation request for that most recent one on the 24th.

Speaker 1: OK.

Speaker 2: So once that's confirmed, I'll be able to issue a refund at $63.95.

Speaker 1: OK.

Speaker 2: OK.

Speaker 1: Now, the prescription as a whole, Mr. Henderson, like I said, you're not required to get this every month.

Speaker 2: If you wanted, you could put a pause on it.

Speaker 1: And then you could just call in and place refill orders as needed.

Speaker 2: OK.

Speaker 1: So, yeah, so I mean, I want to cancel it all together.

Speaker 2: Could you say that again? It broke up there.

Speaker 1: Oh, OK.

Speaker 2: I want to cancel this prescription all together.

Speaker 1: Just cancel it.

Speaker 2: OK.

Speaker 1: So you just did it here.

Speaker 2: Yeah, sure.

Speaker 1: Not a problem.

Speaker 2: And I might, I might, OK.

Speaker 1: Well, I was going to say here, so was it an effectiveness issue?

Speaker 2: You said you wanted to try it.

Speaker 1: Yes, I just wanted to, yes.

Speaker 2: Did you have any interest in trying the AGV by chance, which is more effective?

Speaker 1: That's what I ordered, but that ain't what I got.

Speaker 2: Interesting, because right here, what I see is a prescription was written from the doctor with a generic sildenafil.

Speaker 1: If you want the AGV, I can get you the replacements for free, and then you can actually try those.

Speaker 2: Yes, that's what I ordered, but when it came, it wasn't what I got.

Speaker 1: OK, because I look, I see here the order was placed online, and it looks like the sildenafil was selected.

Speaker 2: But it's an easy adjustment, so I apologize for that.

Speaker 1: Let me, so like I said, so I canceled that most recent one.

Speaker 2: Let me get you replacement AGVs.

Speaker 1: I'll get you quantity of 10, so it'll be a full replacement from that initial order, all right?

Speaker 2: I can do that courtesy for you here.

Speaker 1: And then what I'll do here is I'll put your account on a pause,

Speaker 2: so then if you like it, you can just give us a call back and let us know how it worked for you.

Speaker 1: OK.

Speaker 2: OK.

Speaker 1: We're going to go ahead and put that request in.

Speaker 2: OK.

Speaker 1: Mr. Henderson, is there anything else I can do for you?

Speaker 2: No.

Speaker 1: So, that's going to be the same, well, you canceled the other one, right?

Speaker 2: Correct.

Speaker 1: Yep.

Speaker 2: So I canceled the other one.

Speaker 1: All right.

Speaker 2: And then I'm sending you the Viagra AGV.

Speaker 1: OK.

Speaker 2: And you can try that.

Speaker 1: OK.

Speaker 2: Is that just a trial or?

Speaker 1: So this is the initial, this is an active prescription.

Speaker 2: So we can't do trials with FDA approved medications.

Speaker 1: So what this is, is a replacement, I switched your prescription altogether to the AGV, should you like it.

Speaker 2: OK?

Speaker 1: So this script will have 11 more refills that you have accessible to if you'd like.

Speaker 2: But I went ahead and paused it, so you're not going to get anything monthly.

Speaker 1: OK.

Speaker 2: But if you like, you can just give us a call back and then you can place refill orders.

Speaker 1: OK.

Speaker 2: So that's the, it's going to be the same price as what I had initially?

Speaker 1: Yeah, yeah.

Speaker 2: So it would be $63.95 if you wanted to order it in the future, but this is going to be for free.

Speaker 1: OK.

Speaker 2: OK.

Speaker 1: OK?

Speaker 2: I can work with that, yes.

Speaker 1: OK, that'll do it.

Speaker 2: All right.

Speaker 1: You got it.

Speaker 2: OK.

Speaker 1: Thank you.

Speaker 2: You're welcome.

Speaker 1: Thank you.
